      "comment": "JAYLA MAGIC (7) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 440m behind Wax And Wash (25.08) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has ability and is a key runner. BIG TED (4) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (25.33) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Can figure in the finish. SLOY WAVE (1) was below best at his last start when 8th at this track following a second place finish (24.97) there two back. Must be included in calculations. REVVED UP (8) won as punters' elect last time – another big run is on the cards.",
